{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8fd3b092-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2520"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2520"},"text":"§ 2520.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Military training and service exemption","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding the provisions of any other law or regulation, service in the Peace Corps as a volunteer shall not in any way exempt such volunteer from the performance of any obligations or duties under the provisions of the Universal Military Training and Service Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3801"},"text":"50 U.S.C. 3801","children":[],"tail":" et seq.]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8fd3b093-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/293/tI/s23"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–293, title I, § 23","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-09-22"},"text":"Sept. 22, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/624"},"text":"75 Stat. 624","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8fd3b094-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8fd3b095-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id8fd3b096-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Universal Military Training and Service Act, referred to in text, subsequently renamed the Military Selective Service Act, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-06-24/ch625"},"text":"act June 24, 1948, ch. 625","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/604"},"text":"62 Stat. 604","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 49 (§ 3801 et seq.) of Title 50, War and National Defense. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
